# SeniorPath — Learning Platform

## What This App Is
A self-contained engineering learning platform. No external resources needed. Goal: take a developer from zero to Senior Engineer, Engineering Manager, and CTO across 9 modules. Every explanation, example, production demo, and hands-on project lives here.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 15 (App Router, Turbopack)
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui components
- **Auth/DB**: Supabase (auth + progress tracking)
- **AI Tutor**: Anthropic Claude API (`/api/ai/chat`, `/api/ai/explain`, `/api/ai/hint`, `/api/ai/review`)
- **Code Playgrounds**: Sandpack (`@codesandbox/sandpack-react`)
- **Syntax Highlighting**: `react-syntax-highlighter` (atomOneDark/atomOneLight)
- **Markdown**: `react-markdown` + `remark-gfm`

## Routes
```
/                                    → Home page (9 module cards)
/learn                               → Redirects to /learn/ai-engineering
/learn/[moduleId]                    → Module overview page (lesson list)
/learn/[moduleId]/[lessonId]         → Lesson viewer (sidebar + content)
/api/ai/chat                         → Streaming Claude AI tutor
/api/ai/explain, /hint, /review      → Claude lesson helpers
```

