## ContentBlock Format
Lessons use a `ContentBlock[]` array. Four types:
```typescript
{ type: 'text', markdown: string }
{ type: 'code', language, filename?, code, explanation? }
{ type: 'callout', tone: 'tip'|'warning'|'info'|'production'|'important', title?, content }
{ type: 'exercise', title, description, starterCode, language, solution, hints? }
```

