## Coding Conventions
- All lesson content lives in `src/data/lessons/[moduleId]/` as TypeScript files
- Lesson `id` must match `lessonIds` array in the corresponding `PhaseInfo` in `src/data/modules.ts`
- All lesson files export a typed `Lesson[]` array
- No hardcoded hex colors — use Tailwind classes
- Server components for pages, 'use client' only when needed (CodeBlock, ContentRenderer, Sidebar)
